<LegalLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Bright July"
  description="Privacy Policy for the Bright July website."
  canonical="/privacy"
  heading="Privacy Policy"
  updated="May 20, 2026"
>
  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>This website is a prototype or demonstration environment provided for evaluation and collaboration purposes.</p>
  <p>This Privacy Policy explains how information may be collected and used in connection with the Prototype.</p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We may collect:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>contact information voluntarily provided by users,</li>
    <li>account or authentication details,</li>
    <li>browser and device information,</li>
    <li>IP addresses,</li>
    <li>usage and interaction data,</li>
    <li>diagnostic and technical logs.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Prototype Environment Notice</h2>
  <p>The Prototype may use test systems, mock functionality, or non-production infrastructure.</p>
  <p>Please do not submit:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>sensitive personal information,</li>
    <li>regulated data,</li>
    <li>financial information,</li>
    <li>passwords unrelated to the Prototype,</li>
    <li>or confidential customer data</li>
  </ul>
  <p>unless expressly authorized.</p>

  <h2>Use of Information</h2>
  <p>Information collected may be used to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>provide and operate the Prototype,</li>
    <li>monitor performance and security,</li>
    <li>improve functionality and usability,</li>
    <li>communicate regarding testing and feedback,</li>
    <li>and support product development activities.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Analytics and Logging</h2>
  <p>We may use analytics, monitoring, and logging tools to evaluate usage, troubleshoot issues, and improve the Prototype experience.</p>

  <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
  <p>Information may be shared with service providers or infrastructure partners supporting hosting, analytics, authentication, or technical operations related to the Prototype.</p>
  <p>We do not sell personal information collected through this Prototype.</p>

  <h2>Security</h2>
  <p>Reasonable administrative and technical safeguards may be used; however, the Prototype may not implement all security measures available in production environments.</p>

  <h2>Retention</h2>
  <p>Information collected through the Prototype may be retained only as long as reasonably necessary for evaluation, testing, security, or development purposes.</p>

  <h2>Changes</h2>
  <p>This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>For privacy-related questions, contact:</p>
  <p><a href="mailto:contact@luxihealth.com.au">contact@luxihealth.com.au</a></p>
</LegalLayout>
